<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .order-details {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Thank you for your order!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi there,</p>
      <p>Weâ€™ve received your order. Below are your order details:</p>

      <div class="order-details">
        <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= orderDetails._id %></p>
        <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= orderDetails.createdAt %></p>
        <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> Rs<%= orderDetails.amount %></p>
      </div>

      <p>If you have any questions about your order, feel free to contact us.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you !</p>
      <p>Contact us at printzone@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
